#bold[#magenta[Extended usage information:]]

  Disable options with #cyan[--no-option] e.g. #cyan[--no-watch]

  #bold[connect]]

    #cyan[--no-qrcode]
      Do not open the QR code in a separate browser window.

    #cyan[--livereload]
      Use (experimental) live reloading.

    #cyan[--watch <path>]
      Watch additional directories for changes.

    #cyan[--watchExclude <matcher>]
      Ignore files from watching.
